high_descs: Go in to the kitchen in front of you and go to the fridge.
Take the kettle out of the refrigerator.
Turn left and go to the shelf on your right.
Put the tea kettle on the bookshelf on the bottom shelf close to the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a tea Kettle on a Shelf.

high_descs: Turn around turn right go straight to the fridge
Take the kettle from the fridge
Turn around  go straight walk near to the shelf
Place the kettle on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Take the kettle from the fridge and Place the kettle on the shelf

high_descs: Turn right and turn left to the fridge.
Pick the kettle from the fridge.
Place the kettle on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: To place the kettle on the shelf.
